I can see the issue now. In the CSS file, there's a rule that adds underline on hover for all links within cards:

```css
.card a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}
```

I'll modify the CSS to prevent the underlining on hover for the card links while keeping the cursor as a pointer. I'll update the style.css file:

